EME- electromagnetic environment

EA invloves the use of electromagnetic energy, directed energy, or anti-radiation weapons to attak personnel, facilities, or equipment with the intent of
degrading, neutralizing, or destroying

EP(electromagnetic protection)involves actions taken to protect personnel, facilities, and equipment from any effects of friendly or enemy use of the 
EMS that degrade, neutralize, or destroy friendly combat capability. for ex. EP includes actions takento ensure friendly use of the EMS

ES(electromagnetic support) involves actions tasked by, or under direct control of, an operational commander to search for, inercept, identify, 
and locate or localize

